ials by finishing first in the 50m freestyle and third in the 100m butterfly.\", \"from\": 995, \"to\": 1165, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Dressel\", \"from\": 995, \"to\": 1002}, {\"ngram\": \"two individual events\", \"from\": 1017, \"to\": 1038}, {\"ngram\": \"the 4x100m freestyle relay\", \"from\": 1051, \"to\": 1077}, {\"ngram\": \"the trials\", \"from\": 1082, \"to\": 1092}, {\"ngram\": \"the 50m freestyle\", \"from\": 1115, \"to\": 1132}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100m\", \"from\": 1146, \"to\": 1154}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He's the reigning Olympic champion in both.\", \"from\": 1166, \"to\": 1209, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the reigning Olympic champion\", \"from\": 1171, \"to\": 1200}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dressel also won gold in the 100m freestyle at the Tokyo Olympics, but he failed to qualify for the event this time around after placing third.\", \"from\": 1211, \"to\": 1354, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Dressel\", \"from\": 1211, \"to\": 1218}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 1228, \"to\": 1232}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100m freestyle\", \"from\": 1236, \"to\": 1254}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Olympics\", \"from\": 1258, \"to\": 1276}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 1307, \"to\": 1316}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The other American swimmers headed to Paris to defend individual titles areBobby Finke, the reigning 800m and 1500m freestyles champion, andChase Kalisz, the reigning 400m individual medley champion.\", \"from\": 1356, \"to\": 1555, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1366, \"end\": 1374, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.7734607621868907, \"rank\": 0.17810264417698055, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1394, \"end\": 1399, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999998467522009, \"rank\": 1.5324782677626